#: ../../source/process/asset-guidelines.rst:140
msgid ""
"Ensure there is around 31px of “white space” between the contents of the "
"screenshot and the edge of the screengrab. (This can be adjusted by "
"resizing the rectangle layer below the screengrab in Photoshop)."
